Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne ke kallon shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar mai cike da tausayi a kan tashoshin talabijin shida a ranar Alhamis, daga mai neman kujerar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh da Kristiyan Blasey Ford, matar da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin da ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980.
A halin yanzu, rikicin siyasa ya ci gaba, tare da masu watsa shirye-shirye na katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don jujjuyawar ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi wa FBI don gudanar da binciken mako guda.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa tana da tabbacin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade cikin maye kuma ya yi kokarin cire mata tufafinta a wani bikin makaranta.
Kavanaugh, cikin shaidar da ya bayar da himma, ya ce yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Wataƙila fiye da mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli wannan fim ɗin a ranar Jumma'a, in ji Nielsen.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Ba a samu bayanai nan take ba game da sauran gidajen watsa labarai da suka nuna wannan, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yana da wuya a wasu lokatai ya auna mutanen da suke kallo a ofisoshi.
Don a kwatanta shi, wannan taron jama'a ne da ya kai na wasan ƙwallon ƙafa ko na bikin ba da kyautar kyautar Academy.
Kamfanin Fox News Channel, wanda masu sauraronsa suka goyi bayan Kavanaugh, ya ci gaba da samun matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin zaman, Nielsen ya ce.
ABC ta kasance ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS ta samu miliyan 3.1 da NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 da kuma CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52, in ji Nielsen.
