Haɗa kuɗi zai iya ninka damar samun babban ci gaban AI a Amurka, Lee ya ce a cikin wata hira da CNBC a wannan makon.
Lee, wanda littafinsa "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" da Houghton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa a wannan watan, shi ne HUB na Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a cikin daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin AI a China, Face++.
A cikin shekarun 1980 a Jami'ar Carnegie Mellon, ya yi aiki a kan tsarin AI wanda ya doke mafi kyawun ɗan wasan Othello na Amurka kuma daga baya ya kasance babban jami'in gudanarwa a Microsoft Research kuma shugaban reshen China na Google.
Lee ya amince da gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka da ta gabata, kamar Gasar Robotics ta Hukumar Ci Gaban Bincike ta Tsaro, kuma ya tambayi lokacin da za a ci gaba, don taimakawa wajen gano hangen nesa na gaba.
