Lokacin taron Trump na West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron zaben da aka yi a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurruka biyar da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Da aka samu kuri'ar amincewa da aka yi a yanzu, domin zaɓen da ya yi na cika gurbin da ke gaban Kotun Koli, Trump yana son ya gina goyon baya ga zaben fidda gwani da ke tafe, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar asarar iko a kan majalisa a lokacin da za a kada kuri'ar a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana kuma yaya za a iya kallonsa a kan layi?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, an shirya shi ne a karfe 7 na dare, Satumba, 29 ga watan Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kai tsaye a ƙasa.
Trump zai mai da hankali ne a wannan makon kan sauraron wanda aka nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun koli, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya samu damuwa kan zargin cin zarafin jima'i da ake sa ran za a tabbatar da shi, wanda aka tsare har zuwa mako guda yayin da FBI ke bincike.
Amma, ainihin abin da ya sa ake yin wannan taron ya fi na sauran shi ne don a taimaki 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar ƙalubale a zaɓen da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Kamfanin yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump ya ce, wannan taro na biyar a mako mai zuwa, yana nufin "duba masu sa kai da masu goyon baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjaye da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da kuma majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Samun iko da majalisa na da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa cewa shugaban zai yi tafiya zuwa jihohi da dama idan muka kai lokacin kamfen", in ji wani mai magana da yawun kamfen din Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa, ya shaida wa Reuters.
Taron da za a yi yau da dare, da aka shirya don filin wasan Westbanco a Wheeling, zai iya jawo magoya baya daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma za a iya rufe shi a kafofin watsa labarai a Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia karo na biyu a watan da ya gabata, jihar da ya lashe zaben 2016 da maki sama da 40.
Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya bisa ga tsarin zabe.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don ya ba shi ci gaba a wurin zabe ba", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
