Turai ta fi kowacce kungiya wasa, kuma ta yi nasara sosai a ranar karshe, amma wannan wasa na hudu ya nuna cewa tawagar Amurka tana da ƙarfin gwiwa a fafatawar da wasu suka yi shakku a kai, musamman a gida.
Turai ta yi nasara da maki 10-6 a ranar karshe ta gasar cin kofin Ryder
Turai za ta samu dama mai kyau a ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup bayan ta zo da ci 10-6 daga wasannin kwallon kwando da na hudu na ranar Asabar.
Ƙungiyar Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci harin tare da nasara biyu a kan Tiger Woods mai fama da wahala don ɗaukar ƙimar su zuwa maki huɗu a Le Golf National.
Ƙungiyar Turai ta Thomas Bjorn, da ke ƙoƙarin riƙe kofin da suka rasa a Hazeltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, ta rinjayi wata ƙungiyar Amurka da ta yi rashin daidaito a cikin ƙwallon ƙafa na safe, don haka suka ci wasan 3-1.
Ƙasar Amirka ta fi tsayayya a wasan hudu, ta ci wasanni biyu, amma ba ta bar baya ba.
Ƙungiyar Jim Furyk ta bukaci maki takwas daga wasanni 12 na wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Lahadi don riƙe kofin.
Fleetwood shine farkon dan wasan Turai da ya ci maki hudu a jere yayin da shi da Molinari, wanda aka yi wa lakabi da "Moliwood" bayan karshen mako mai ban mamaki, su ne kawai ma'aurata na biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup da suka ci maki huɗu bayan wasannin su na farko.
Bayan sun murkushe Woods da Patrick Reed a cikin kwallaye huɗu, sun yi wasa tare da kyau don cinye Woods da sabon ɗan Amurka Bryson Dechambreau tare da 5 & 4 da suka fi ƙarfin gaske.
Woods, wanda ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna wasu fitattun abubuwa amma yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 cikin 29 a wasan kwallon kwando da hudu da kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta a lokacin wasan kwallon hudu na safe, ya dawo ya yi wasa tare da Henrik Stenson a cikin wasanni huɗu har zuwa 2&1 a kan Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka - waɗanda ke matsayi na farko da na uku a duniya.
Amma, a rana mai kyau da iska take hurawa daga kudu maso yammacin Paris, ba a ko da yaushe Turai take samun ma'ana ba.
Jordan Spieth wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku da Justin Thomas sun kafa wa Amurkawa alama da maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun ci nasara 2&1 mai wahala akan Spain Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin kwallaye huɗu kuma daga baya suka dawo don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy da 3&4 a cikin wasanni huɗu bayan sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko.
Sau biyu kawai a tarihin Ryder Cup, wata ƙungiya ta dawo daga ragamar maki huɗu lokacin da suka shiga wasan ƙwallon ƙafa, kodayake ƙungiyar Furyk tana buƙatar wasa daidai don riƙe kofin saboda sun riga sun riƙe shi.
Amma, bayan sun yi kwanaki biyu suna matsayi na biyu, ba su da tabbacin cewa za su iya yin yaƙi a ranar Lahadi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta "daina" kawar da makamai ba
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya gaya wa Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumi zai ƙara tsananta musu wajen amincewa da Amurka kuma babu shakka ba za ta daina amfani da makaman nukiliya ba.
Ri Yong Ho ya gaya wa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na shekara-shekara cewa a cikin shekarar da ta shige, Koriya ta Arewa ta ɗauki "matakai masu kyau na alheri", kamar su dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da kuma na makamai masu linzami, rushe filin gwajin nukiliya, da kuma alkawarin ba za ta ƙara yawan makaman nukiliya da kuma fasahar nukiliya ba.
"Amma ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba", in ji shi.
"Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba, babu amincewa da tsaron kasa, kuma a irin wannan yanayi, ba za mu kasance farkon masu sassaucin ra'ayi ba".
Yayin da Ri ya maimaita sanannun korafe-korafen Koriya ta Arewa game da kin amincewa da Washington da "matakan" na kawar da makaman nukiliya wanda zai ba Koriya ta Arewa lada idan ta ɗauki matakai na mataki-mataki, maganarsa ta yi kama da ma'ana domin ba ta yi watsi da kawar da makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi nuni da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa da Kim Jong-un da Donald Trump suka fitar a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a ranar 12 ga Yuni a Singapore, lokacin da Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don "rushe makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa.
Koriya ta Arewa na son kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta daina makaman nukiliya.
Har ila yau, Washington ta yi tsayayya da neman sassauta takunkumin kasa da kasa kan Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta nace kan "hallaka makaman nukiliya da farko" kuma ta kara matsa lamba ta hanyar kara matakan takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar da ta dace, har ma ta yi watsi da 'yankan-tsaki na kawo karshen yaki,'" in ji Ri.
"Halin da ake ciki cewa takunkumi na iya sa mu durƙusa mafarki ne na mutanen da ba su san mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, ci gaba da takunkumi yana ƙara sa mu baƙin ciki.
Ri bai ce komai ba game da shirin wani taron koli na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump wanda shugaban Amurka ya jawo hankali a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a farkon makon.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya mai da hankali ga tarurruka uku da Kim ya yi da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ya daɗa cewa: "Idan da Koriya ta Kudu ce ta shiga cikin wannan batun na kawar da makaman nukiliya ba Amurka ba, da ba za a sami irin wannan rashin ƙarfi a kawar da makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya ba.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na shekarar da ta gabata, lokacin da ya gaya wa Babban Taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba makawa ne cewa makamai masu linzami na Koriya ta Arewa za su kai hari ga ƙasar Amurka bayan "Mista muguwar Shugaba" Trump ya kira Kim "mai harbi" a kan aikin kashe kansa.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda bara ya yi barazanar "hallaka" Koriya ta Arewa, ya yaba wa Kim sosai saboda ƙarfin hali da ya nuna wajen daukar matakan kawar da makaman, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi, kuma takunkumi na bukatar ci gaba har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kawar da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da lokacin da zai yi hakan, yana mai cewa "Ba kome ba ko shekara biyu, uku ko watanni biyar".
Kasar Sin da Rasha sun yi imanin cewa ya kamata kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya saka wa Pyongyang saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Amma, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amirka, Mike Pompeo, ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumi ta Kwamitin Tsaro da himma kuma ba tare da tsayawa ba har sai mun kai ga kammala, ƙarshe, tabbataccen halakar makaman nukiliya".
Tun daga shekarar 2006, kwamitin sulhu ya tsaurara takunkumin da ya kafa kan Koriya ta Arewa a wani yunkuri na dakile kudaden da ake baiwa Pyongyang don harkokin nukiliya da kuma makamai masu linzami.
Pompeo ya gana da Ri a wajen babban taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, bayan haka ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron koli na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekara, amma tafiyarsa ta karshe ba ta tafi daidai ba.
Ya bar Pyongyang a watan Yuli, ya ce an samu ci gaba, amma sa'o'i kaɗan bayan haka, Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge shi da yin "da'awa mai ban haushi".
A wani taro da Moon ya yi, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin rushe makaman nukiliya da kuma gina makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki "matakai masu dacewa".
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "matakan da suka dace" da yake son gani su ne tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya yi alkawari a Singapore da kuma matakan daidaita dangantaka da Washington.
Daliban Harvard sun yi darasi game da samun isashen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Harvard a wannan shekara ya ba wa dukan ɗalibansa na digiri na biyu ƙarin barci a ƙoƙarin ƙin al'adun karatu na macho da ke ƙaruwa ta wurin yin amfani da kofi a "dukan dare".
Wani masanin ilimi ya gano cewa ɗalibai a manyan jami'o'i na duniya sau da yawa ba su da ilimi game da ainihin yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a fannin maganin barci a Makarantar Kiwon Lafiya ta Harvard kuma ƙwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women, ya tsara wannan darasi, wanda ya gaskata shi ne na farko na irin wannan a Amirka.
Ya fara wannan darasi ne bayan ya ba da jawabi game da tasirin rashin barci a kan ilmantarwa.
'A ƙarshen taron, wata yarinya ta zo wurina, ta ce, 'Me ya sa suka gaya mini wannan yanzu, a shekarata ta ƙarshe?'
Ta ce ba a taɓa gaya mata muhimmancin barci ba - abin da ya ba ni mamaki,' in ji shi a cikin The Telegraph.
Wannan darasi da aka gabatar a wannan shekarar, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai muhimman abubuwa game da yadda yin barci da kyau yake taimaka wa ɗalibai su yi nasara a makaranta da kuma wasanni, da kuma yadda yake inganta lafiyarsu.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin ilimin halayyar ɗan adam a Makarantar Kiwon Lafiya ta Harvard kuma shugaban jami'ar kula da lafiyar jama'a, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da wannan darasi ne bayan an gano cewa ɗalibai suna fama da rashin barci sosai a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya yana ɗauke da wasu ayyuka masu ma'ana.
A wani sashe, akwai hoton ɗakin kwana inda ɗalibai suke danna kofuna na kofi, labule, takalma na motsa jiki, da littattafai don su gaya musu game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar wasan motsa jiki da kuma muhimmancin yin barci.
A wani sashe kuma, an gaya wa masu halarta yadda yin barci na dogon lokaci zai iya ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Taswirar harabar makarantar, tare da gumaka masu ma'ana, ta ƙarfafa masu halarta su yi tunani game da rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum.
'Mun san cewa hakan ba zai canja halayen ɗalibai nan take ba.
Amma mun gaskata cewa suna da hakkin su sani - kamar yadda kuke da hakkin ku san sakamakon shan sigari a kan lafiyarku,' in ji Farfesa Czeisler.
Al'adar 'koyon dare' har ila tana nan, ya ce, yana ƙara da cewa fasaha ta zamani da matsi mai yawa da ake yi wa ɗalibai ya sa rashin barci ya zama matsala mai girma.
Ya ce, tabbata cewa kana samun isashen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama "makamin sirri" na ɗalibi don kauce wa matsi, gajiya, da kuma damuwa - har ma don kauce wa samun nauyi, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwa ta kasance cikin yanayin yunwa, wanda ke sa ka ji yunwa a kowane lokaci.
Raymond So, ɗan shekara 19 da ke California da ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da kuma ilimin halittu, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Czeisler ya tsara wannan darasin bayan ya halarci ɗaya daga cikin darussansa a shekara ta farko a Harvard a bara.
Ya ce wannan darasin ya buɗe masa idanu kuma ya sa ya soma nazarin Littafi Mai Tsarki a dukan makarantar.
Mataki na gaba, ya yi fata, shi ne a gaya wa dukan ɗaliban digiri su kammala irin wannan tsarin karatu kafin su shiga cikin wannan cibiyar da mutane suke gasa da juna.
Farfesa Czeisler ya ba da shawara cewa ɗalibai su yi la'akari da kafa ƙararrawa don lokacin barci da kuma lokacin farkawa, kuma su san cewa 'blue light' da ke fitowa daga fuskokin lantarki da kuma fitilun LED na iya ɓata tsarin circadian da ke sa mutum ya yi ƙoƙari ya taɓa tumaki.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: Manufar Menga ta ci sojojin Gerrard
Rangers sun sake fuskantar wani mummunan yanayi na rashin jin daɗi lokacin da Dolly Menga ta ci Steven Gerrard ta tawagar da ba ta da jituwa ta ci 1-0.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta nemi nasarar farko a matsayin baƙi tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da suka yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holt ya ba Gerrard komawarsa ta biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin manajan don haka ƙungiyarsa ta kasance maki takwas a baya Hearts, wanda ya yi nasara a cikin Ladbrokes Premiership.
Menga ya ci kwallo ne minti bakwai kafin lokacin hutu, kuma ba ya ganin tawagar Rangers za ta yi wasa ba tare da samun kwarin gwiwa ba.
Yanzu Rangers sun sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingston ya hau zuwa na uku kuma yana bin Hibernian a raga.
Kuma za a iya samun ƙarin matsala ga Rangers bayan da aka yi wa mai shari'a Calum Spence jinya saboda raunin da ya ji a kai bayan da aka jefa wani abu daga gefe.
Gerrand ya yi canje-canje takwas a tawagar da ta tsallake Ayr zuwa wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
Holt, a gefe guda, yana amfani da Livi-11 wanda ya ɗauki maki daga Hearts a makon da ya gabata kuma zai kasance cikin damuwa game da yadda tawagarsa da aka horar da su suka kashe abokan hamayyarsu a kowane juyi.
Rangers na iya mamaye mallakar kwallon, amma Livingston ya yi fiye da haka lokacin da suke da kwallon.
Da sun yi maki ne bayan minti biyu da jefa kwallo ta farko da Menga ta yi, Scott Pittman ya ci Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan ya yi nasara.
Keaghan Jacobs ya jefa wa kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma abokin wasansa Alan Lithgow ya kasa buga kwallo a raga.
Rangers sun ci gaba da wasa, amma a wasan karshe, sun fi mai da hankali ga yadda suke wasa.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji cewa ya kamata a jefa masa kwallo a wasan da ya yi da Steven Lawless, amma mai wasan kwaikwayo Steven Thomson ya yi watsi da roƙon Colombian.
Rangers sun yi nasarar samun harbi biyu kawai a raga a farkon rabin wasan amma tsohon mai tsaron raga na Ibrox Liam Kelly ya sha wahala daga ci gaban Lassana Coulibaly da kuma ci gaba da Ovie Ejaria.
Ko da yake Livi ya buɗe ƙwallo a minti na 34 yana iya zama a kan hanyar wasan, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan, ko da kuwa saboda aikinsu ne kawai.
Ranger ya sake kasa yin amfani da Jacobs mai zurfi.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya aika da kwallon zuwa Scott Robinson, wanda ya kasance mai nutsuwa kuma ya aika da shi zuwa Menga don sauƙin kammala.
Gerrard ya yi aiki a lokacin hutu lokacin da ya yi musayar Coulibaly don Ryan Kent kuma musayar ta sami kusan tasiri nan take lokacin da gefen ya aika zuwa Morelos amma ya kori Kelly mai ban sha'awa daga layinsa zuwa block.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tilasta wa baƙi su yi wasa daidai da irin wasan da suke so, Lithgow da Halkett suna yin dogon ƙwallo bayan dogon ƙwallo.
Holt's team zai iya kara musu nasara a karshen matakai, amma McGregor ya tashi da kyau don dakatar da Jacobs kafin Lithgow ya iya shiga daga kusurwa.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers Glenn Middleton yana da wata da'awar da aka yi a baya don bugun bugun bugun da ya yi da Jacobs, amma Thomson ya sake dubawa.
Almanac: Wanda Ya Ƙirƙiri Geiger
Kuma yanzu shafi daga littafinmu na "Lahadi da safe": 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekara 136 da ta shige, kuma MU KARANTA DAGA ... ranar da aka haifi ɗan kimiyya na nan gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙiri wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna aikin rediyo, abin da ya kai ga na'urar da ake kira Geiger counter.
Tun daga lokacin, Geiger counter ya kasance ginshiƙi na kimiyya, kuma ya zama ginshiƙi a al'adun gargajiya, kamar a cikin fim din 1950 "Bells of Coronado", wanda ya yi wasa da waɗannan masana kimiyya biyu masu ban mamaki Roy Rogers da Dale Evans:
Mutum: "Mece ce wannan?"
Rogers: "Gidan Geiger ne da ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo, kamar su uranium.
Sa'ad da ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da atoms suke yi daga aikin rediyo da ke cikin ma'adinai.
Evans: "Ya Ubangiji, wannan yana karya yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945, 'yan kwanaki kafin ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma abin da ya yi ya ci gaba da rayuwa.
