Da yake fitowa a matsayin mai ƙin yarda a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "ƙasa" fiye da kowa yayin da yake girma, domin "ba a yarda da son yara maza da mata ba.
Ya ce: "Har wa yau, waɗannan jiye-jiye na rashin, da kuma bambancin, su ne ainihin abubuwan da suka ba ni ƙarfi da kuzari na cim ma nasara".
Ya ce yana son ya tabbatar da cewa shi "wani abu ne", don kada ya sa kowa ya yi sanyin gwiwa sa'ad da suka gano cewa shi ɗan jima'i ne.
Ta zama babbar 'yar wasan LGBT kuma ta yi amfani da bayyanarta a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Australia don yin kira ga kasashe da yawa da su yanke hukunci game da luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi ƙarya game da yadda yake ji domin yana farin cikin kasancewa a bayyane ba tare da sakamako ba kuma yana son ya ba wa wasu "bege".
Gwarzon dan wasan duniya sau uku ya ce "ya kama shi da damuwa" saboda ya ƙaunaci wani dan wasan fim din Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013.
Daley ya auri wanda ya lashe Oscar a bara, wanda ya girme shi da shekaru 20, amma ya ce bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da kake fuskantar abubuwa masu yawa a irin wannan ƙuruciya"  ya je wasannin Olympics na farko yana ɗan shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka  ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan shekara ɗaya da ya fuskanci irin wannan tashin hankali da rashin ƙarfi.
A watan Yuni, ma'auratan suka haifi ɗa mai suna Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ta ce "dukkanin ra'ayinta" ya canja.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da ya kasance shi ne 'Ina bukatar in lashe lambar zinare,'" in ji shi.
"Amma, ka sani, akwai abubuwa da suka fi lambobin zinare na wasannin Olympics.
Robbie ne lambar zinare ta gasar Olympics".
Sunan ɗansa ya yi kama da na mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekara 40 bayan an gano cewa yana da ciwon kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda da cewa zai mutu ba kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya tambaya shi ne ko suna da tikiti na London 2012  domin yana son ya kasance a layin gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba cewa 'Ba za ka kasance a nan ba domin ka kasance a gaba ba, Baba,'" in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa sa'ad da ya daina numfashi, kuma bayan ya daina numfashi kuma ya mutu ne na fahimci cewa ba shi da iko", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daley ya shiga gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
"Na san cewa wannan shi ne abin da na yi mafarki na tsawon rayuwata - yin iyo a gaban jama'ar gidana a wasannin Olympics, babu wani abin da ya fi wannan", in ji shi.
Hakanan ya ba da waƙar farko  Proud ta Heather Small  wanda kuma ya yi ma'ana tare da shi a cikin shiri na Olympics kuma har yanzu yana ba shi kaza.
