Jamus ta sabon warship sake jinkirta
An shirya sabon jirgin ruwan sojin Jamus ya fara aiki a 2014 domin maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba zai kasance ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa, saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma karuwar kudade, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na kasar.
An dage fara aiki da "Rheinland-Pfalz", babban jirgin ruwan sabon Baden-Wuerttemberg-class frigates zuwa farkon rabin 2019, a cewar jaridar Die Zeit tana mai ambaton wani kakakin soji.
Wannan jirgin ya kamata ya shiga rundunar sojin ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da ake fuskanta bayan isar da shi sun shafi wannan babban aikin.
Jirgin ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Wuerttemberg da Navy ta ba da umarni a 2007 za su maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwan Bremen.
An fahimci cewa za su sami babban bindiga, makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da kuma wasu fasahohi na sirri kamar rage radar, infrared da kuma sautin sauti.
Sauran mahimman fasalulluka sun haɗa da tsawon lokacin kulawa  ya kamata ya yiwu a tura sabbin jirage masu saukar ungulu har zuwa shekaru biyu daga gida.
Amma jinkiri na ci gaba yana nufin cewa jiragen yaƙi masu ci gaba  da za su ba wa Jamus damar yin amfani da ƙarfinta a ƙasashen waje  za su zama marasa amfani a lokacin da za su fara aiki, in ji Die Zeit.
Frigate mai suna F125 da ta yi hatsari ta yi ta zama sanadiyar labarai a shekarar da ta gabata sa'ad da rundunar sojin ruwa ta Jamus ta ƙi ta ba da izinin yin amfani da jirgin kuma ta tura shi zuwa tashar jiragen ruwa ta Blohm & Voss a Hamburg.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko da Sojojin Ruwa suka mayar da jirgin bayan sun kai shi ga wani mai gina jirgin.
Ba a san abin da ya sa aka mayar da jirgin ba, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ce wasu muhimman "rashin ingantattun kayan aiki da na'urori" sun sa jirgin ba zai iya amfani da shi ba idan aka tura shi cikin wani kamfen.
Rashin ingancin software yana da mahimmanci musamman tunda jiragen Baden-Wuerttemberg-class zasu kasance masu sarrafawa mutanen da ke da matukan jirgi kimanin 120  rabin ma'aikata ne kawai akan tsofaffin jiragen ruwan Bremen.
An kuma gano cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda ke rage aikinsa kuma yana rage ikon Sojojin Ruwa na ƙara haɓaka a nan gaba.
An yi imanin cewa tan 7,000 na "Rheinland-Pfalz" sun ninka na jiragen ruwa iri ɗaya da Jamus ta yi amfani da su a Yaƙin Duniya na Biyu sau biyu.
Baya ga kayan aikin da ba daidai ba, farashin farashin duk aikin  ciki har da horar da ma'aikatan  ma ya shafi batun.
Wannan ya kai  biliyan 3.1 ($3.6 biliyan)  fiye da na farko  biliyan 2.2.
Matsalolin da sababbin jiragen ruwa suke fuskanta sun zama masu muhimmanci musamman a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan da aka yi gargadin cewa ƙarfin rundunar sojan Jamus yana raguwa.
A farkon wannan shekara, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokoki ta Jamus, ya yarda cewa "jirgin ruwan na kasa da ke da iko ya fara ƙarewa.
Jami'in ya ce batun ya daɗa muni da shigewar lokaci, tun da an dakatar da tsofaffin jiragen ruwa, amma ba a ba da wasu don maye gurbin su ba.
Ya yi gunaguni cewa babu wani daga cikin rukunin Baden-Wuerttemberg da zai iya shiga rundunar.
