Birtaniya za ta "yi nadama har abada" idan ta rasa matsayinta na jagorar masana'antar kera motoci a duniya bayan Brexit, in ji Sakataren Ayyuka Greg Clark.
Ya kara da cewa "abin damuwa ne" Toyota UK ta shaida wa BBC cewa idan Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba, za ta dakatar da samar da kayayyaki a kamfanin da ke Burnaston, kusa da Derby.
"Muna bukatar yarjejeniya", in ji Mr. Clark.
Kamfanin kera motoci na Japan ya ce tasirin jinkirin kan iyakoki na iya janye ayyukan ma'aikata idan aka samu yarjejeniya ba tare da yarjejeniya ba.
Shirin na Burnaston  wanda ke kera Toyota Auris da Avensis  ya samar da motoci kusan 150,000 a shekarar da ta gabata, 90% daga cikinsu an fitar da su zuwa sauran Tarayyar Turai.
"Ra'ayina shi ne idan Birtaniya ta bar EU a ƙarshen Maris, za mu ga an daina samar da kayayyaki a masana'antarmu", in ji Marvin Cooke, manajan Toyota a Burnaston.
Sauran kamfanonin kera motoci na Burtaniya, ciki har da Honda, BMW da Jaguar Land Rover sun yi ta faɗar fargaba game da barin EU ba tare da yarjejeniya ba da kuma yadda cinikayya ta ƙetare za ta yi aiki.
Alal misali, BMW ta ce za ta rufe mini-plant dinta a Oxford na wata daya bayan Brexit.
Babban abin damuwa ya shafi abin da masana'antun motoci ke cewa haɗarin sarkar samarwa ne a cikin yanayin Brexit ba tare da yarjejeniya ba.
Toyota tana aiki ne a kan "a kan lokaci", tare da sassan da ke zuwa kowane minti 37 daga masu samar da kayayyaki a cikin Burtaniya da EU don motocin da aka yi don oda.
Idan Birtaniya ta bar EU ba tare da wata yarjejeniya ba a ranar 29 ga watan Maris, za a iya samun rikici a kan iyakar wanda masana'antu ke cewa zai iya haifar da jinkiri da karancin kayayyaki.
Kamfanin Toyota ya ce ba zai yiwu ba ya ajiye kayayyaki fiye da kwana ɗaya a shingen Derbyshire, saboda haka za a dakatar da samarwa.
Mista Clark ya ce shirin Theresa May na Chequers na dangantaka ta gaba da EU "an tsara shi ne daidai don kauce wa waɗannan bincike a kan iyakar.
"Muna bukatar yarjejeniya. Muna son mafi kyawun yarjejeniya wanda, kamar yadda na ce, zai ba mu damar more nasarar da muke samu a yanzu, amma kuma mu yi amfani da wannan dama", in ji shi a shirin BBC Radio 4 na yau.
"Alamar ba kawai daga Toyota ba, har ma daga wasu masana'antun, ita ce muna bukatar mu ci gaba da abin da ya kasance babban nasara na samar da kayayyaki.
Toyota ba ta iya cewa tsawon lokacin da za a dakatar da samarwa ba, amma ta yi gargadin cewa a cikin dogon lokaci ƙarin farashin zai iya rage gasa ta shuka kuma a ƙarshe ya kashe ayyuka.
Peter Tsouvallaris, wanda ya yi aiki a Burnaston na shekara 24 kuma mai kiran ƙungiyar Unite a wurin, ya ce 'yan ƙungiyar suna ƙara damuwa: "A ganina, idan waɗannan ayyuka suka tafi, ba za su sake dawowa ba.
Wani mai magana da yawun gwamnati ya ce: "Mun gabatar da takamaiman tsari mai ma'ana game da alakarmu ta gaba da EU.
Trump zai iya sake dage ganawar da Rosenstein, Fadar White House ta ce
Taron Donald Trump mai hadari da mataimakin babban lauya Rod Rosenstein na iya "saukewa har mako guda" yayin da ake ci gaba da takarar da aka zaɓa na babban alkalin kotun Brett Kavanaugh, Fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken tsoma baki a zaben Rasha, alaƙar da ke tsakanin masu taimakon Trump da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar haramta dokar da shugaban ya yi.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan ko a'a, kuma hakan zai yi barazana ga 'yancin Mueller, ya ci gaba da zuga jita-jita a Washington na watanni da yawa.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna yiwuwar sanya mai daukar sauti don yin rikodin tattaunawar da Trump, da kuma yiwuwar cire shugaban kasa ta hanyar gyara ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta rahoton.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya je fadar White House, a yayin da aka samu rahotanni cewa yana kan hanyarsa ta komawa.
Maimakon haka, an shirya taro da Trump, wanda ke Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York a lokacin, don ranar Alhamis.
Trump ya ce zai "zaɓa kada ya kori" Rosenstein, amma sai aka dage taron don kauce wa rikici da kotun majalisar dattawa inda Kavanaugh da daya daga cikin matan da suka zarge shi da laifin lalata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford, suka yi shaida.
A ranar Juma'a, Trump ya umarci FBI ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh, kuma ya sake dage zaben majalisar dattawa.
Sakatariyar yada labarai ta Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a Fox News ranar Lahadi.
Lokacin da aka tambaye ta game da taron Rosenstein, ta ce: "Ba a riga an ƙayyade ranar ba, zai iya zama wannan makon, zan iya ganin an sake shi mako guda tare da sauran abubuwan da ke faruwa a Kotun Koli.
Amma za mu gani, kuma ina son in sanar da 'yan jarida".
Wasu 'yan jarida za su ki yarda da wannan bayanin: Sanders bai yi taron manema labarai na fadar White House ba tun ranar 10 ga watan Satumba.
Sai mai masaukinmu Chris Wallace ya tambaye ni dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ta ce rashin isashen labarai ba saboda rashin son 'yan jaridar talabijin da ke da "ta'aziyyar tasiri" ba ne, ko da yake ta ce: "Ba zan yi jayayya da cewa suna da tasiri ba.
Ta yi nuni da cewa za a kara samun hulda kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da manema labarai.
"Shugaban kasa ya yi tambayoyi da amsa fiye da kowane shugaban kasa da ya riga shi", in ji ta, ta daɗa cewa, ba tare da ta faɗi wani tabbaci ba, "mun duba lambobin".
Za a ci gaba da yin taron tattaunawa, Sanders ya ce, amma "idan 'yan jarida suna da zarafin yin tambayoyi kai tsaye ga shugaban Amirka, zai fi kyau su yi magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sosai, kuma kun ga mun yi hakan sosai a cikin 'yan makonnin da suka gabata, kuma zai maye gurbin taron manema labarai da za ku iya yi da shugaban Amurka".
Trump yakan amsa tambayoyi lokacin da ya bar fadar White House ko kuma ya shiga cikin taron jama'a ko kuma sanarwar manema labarai tare da masu daraja masu ziyara.
Ba a yawan samun labarai da aka wallafa a kai a kai.
A wannan makon a New York, shugaban ya nuna dalilin da ya sa, ta hanyar nuna rashin daidaito da kuma lokaci, a gaban 'yan jarida da suka taru.
Sakataren kiwon lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan EU a NHS Scotland game da fargabar Brexit
Sakataren kiwon lafiya ya rubuta wa ma'aikatan EU da ke aiki a NHS na Scotland don nuna godiyar kasar da kuma fatan su ci gaba da zama bayan Brexit.
Jeanne Freeman MSP ta aika da wasika da kasa da watanni shida kafin Birtaniya ta fice daga EU.
Gwamnatin Scotland ta riga ta yi alkawarin biyan kuɗin da aka biya na neman matsayin EU da ke aiki a cikin ayyukan gwamnati.
A cikin wasikar ta, Misis Freeman ta rubuta: "A lokacin bazara, tattaunawar ficewar Birtaniya da EU ta ci gaba, a kan hanyar zuwa yanke shawara da ake tsammani a wannan kaka.
Amma gwamnatin Burtaniya ta kuma kara shirya wa wani yiwuwar rashin yarjejeniya.
Na san cewa lokaci ne mai wuya ga dukanku.
Shi ya sa nake son in sake maimaita yadda nake daraja gudummawar kowane ma'aikaci, ko da kuwa ƙasarsu.
Abokan aiki daga ko'ina cikin EU da kuma bayan, suna kawo kwarewa da basira masu tamani da ke ƙarfafa da inganta aikin kiwon lafiya, kuma yana amfanar marasa lafiya da kuma al'ummomin da muke yi wa hidima.
Scotland gida ce a gare ku, kuma muna son ku zauna a nan.
Christion Abercrombie yana jinyar ciwon kai
Dan wasan Tennessee State Tigers Christion Abercrombie ya yi aikin tiyatar gaggawa bayan ya samu rauni a kan kai a ranar Asabar da ta kai ga cin nasara 31-27 a kan Vanderbilt Commodores, in ji Mike Organ na Tennessee.
Babban kocin Tennessee State Rod Reed ya gaya wa manema labarai cewa raunin ya faru ne jim kadan kafin hutun.
"Ya zo a kan gefen kuma ya yi kama da kawai a can", Reed ya ce.
Masu koyar da Abercrombie da ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun ba shi iskar oxygen a gefen filin kafin a saka shi a kan na'urar daukar hoto kuma a mayar da shi don ƙarin kimantawa.
Wani jami'in jihar Tennessee ya gaya wa Chris Harris na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee cewa Abercrombie ya fito daga gidan wasan kwaikwayo a Cibiyar Kiwon Lafiya ta Vanderbilt.
Harris ya kara da cewa "babu wani bayani game da irin/girman raunin da aka yi" kuma Tennessee na ci gaba da kokarin gano lokacin da raunin ya faru.
Abercrombie, mai shekara biyu a makarantar sakandare, yana cikin kakar wasa ta farko a Tennessee State bayan ya koma daga Illinois.
Ya yi kisa sau biyar kafin ya bar wasan a ranar Asabar, wanda ya kawo jimlarsa na kakar wasa zuwa sau 18.
