Masu sayen ƙasashen waje za su biya ƙarin harajin hatimi lokacin da suka sayi dukiya a Burtaniya, kuma za a yi amfani da ƙarin kuɗin don taimaka wa marasa gida, a ƙarƙashin sabbin tsare-tsaren Tory
Wannan matakin zai kawar da nasarar Corbyn na jan hankalin matasa masu zabe.
