Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesiya
A kalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske da kuma tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Da aka dakatar da sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su iya samun wani bayani daga Donggala Regency, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palu da ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai karfin 7.5.
A Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 zuwa inda babu hadari bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu shine babban birnin lardin Tsakiya Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan mutane 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekara 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala shine regency wanda ya ratsa kan kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin 2017, an kiyasta yawan mutanen Regency, yanki na yanki a ƙarƙashin lardin, ya kai 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune ginshikan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiya Sulawesi, musamman yankin bakin teku na Donggala.
Ma'adinan nickel ma yana da mahimmanci a lardin, amma galibi an maida hankali ne a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da girgizar ruwa sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, in ji Hukumar Sarrafa Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami ya kuma afkawa yammacin Donggala a 1996, ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane tara.
Indonesia tana zaune a kan yankin da ake kira Pacific Ring of Fire kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Ga wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesiya a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga watan Disamba wanda ya haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa kasashe 14 ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta afkawa gaɓar yamma na Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, kusa da gabar Sumatra.
2006: Girman 6.8 ya afkawa kudancin Java, tsibirin Indonesia mafi yawan jama'a, wanda ya haifar da tsunami da ya afkawa gabar kudu kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar kusan 700.
2009: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Fiye da mutane 1,100 suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa ɗaya daga cikin tsibiran Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta jawo tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane 300.
2016: Wani girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya na Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da fargaba yayin da aka tunatar da mutane da hallakar da girgizar kasa da tsunami mai kisa ta 2004 ta yi.
Wannan ba ya kai ga tsunami a wannan lokacin, amma fiye da 100 sun mutu domin gine-gine sun rushe,
2018: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok na Indonesia, inda mutane sama da 500 suka mutu, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta halaka dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makara.
