Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addancin da aka kai a birnin New York wanda ya yi sanadiyar mutuwar mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa a jihar ba saboda wani laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi zargin cewa ya yi amfani da motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a gefen West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan don kashe masu tafiya da ƙafa da kuma mai hawan keke da ke kan hanyarsa a watan Oktoba.
