Duka waɗannan laifuffukan suna ɗauke da hukuncin kisa, in ji takardar kotu.
Makonni bayan harin, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukunci a kan tuhume-tuhume 22, da suka hada da tuhume-tuhume guda takwas na kisan kai domin neman cin hanci, wanda ake amfani da shi a matsayin sanadiyar tuhume-tuhume na tarayya a shari'o'in da suka shafi tarayyar kasa, da kuma na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce, harin ya bukaci "shirye-shirye da kuma tunani sosai", suna kwatanta yadda Saipov ya yi shi da "m, mai zalunci, da kuma lalata".
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa da kuma asarar abokai", in ji sanarwar.
Biyar cikin waɗanda suka mutu 'yan yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Argentina.
